import {useDispatch, useSelector} from "react-redux"; import {useEffect} from "react"; import {deleteBlogs, getBlogs} from "../../services/blogService"; import {Link, useNavigate} from "react-router-dom"; export default function ListBlog (){ const dispatch = useDispatch() const navigate = useNavigate() const blogs = useSelector(state => { return state.blogs.blogs }) useEffect(() =>{ dispatch(getBlogs()) }, []) const handleDelete = ( (id)=>{ dispatch(deleteBlogs(id)).then(()=>{ dispatch(getBlogs()) navigate("/home") }) }) return(
